text: LostI have the  life  people dream about   Wife  kids  house  job   We have our needs covered and for the most part we are ok   THe issue is I am not   Work has beaten me into a shell   I sit here in the early am and the thought of working feels me with dread   I know I am depressed I know i shouldn t be but at the end of the day I have been pulled so thin   I understand my parents now and why they made the choices they did    I recorded good bye videos for my kids and my wife this morning   Honestly it felt good   It feels like closure   I felt like i was on a solid path   I had planned to hang myself   Not the cleanest or easiest death I know but again something I control  i would do it in a place my family didn t have to deal with it   Anyway I got to it and I chickened out of the pain to come   I know it is short term pain but I didn t want it   Maybe I am failing at even this   I dont know    I just don t have anyone to reach out to   Honestly if i talk to my wife she panics about our lifestyle and so on    I don t sleep  I don t eat   I am ready to move on as it were   See what s next   My kids would be young enough they would get over it     I won t lie the feeling of control and closure was the best i have felt in months   All it needed was one last step and I failed and now it is back to dread and pain
summary: Wife has a job, kids have a house job, they have their needs covered. Work has beaten him into a shell. He recorded good bye videos for his kids and his wife this morning. He had planned to hang himself but chickened out.
